* {{ill|Daimyojin Shrine|ja|大名持神社|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Daimyojin Shrine|qq=}}
* {{ill|Seki Shrine|ja|塞神社|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Seki Shrine|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}}

